msgid ""
"IT SEEMS AS IF THIS THEME HAS BEEN MANUALLY DOWNLOADED INSTEAD OF VIA THIS "
"THEME DOWNLOADER. A FRESH DOWNLOAD IS REQUIRED AND THE OLD THEME DIRECTORY "
"\"%s\" WILL BE RENAMED TO \"%s_DISABLED\""
msgstr ""
"ČINI SE KAO DA JE OVA TEMA RUČNO PREUZETA UMJESTO PREKO OVOG PROGRAMA ZA "
"PREUZIMANJE TEMA. POTREBNO JE NOVO PREUZIMANJE I STARI DIREKTOR TEME \"%s\" "
"ĆE BIT PREIMENOVAN U \"%s_DISABLED\""

msgid "DOWNLOADING THEME"
msgstr "PREUZIMANJE TEME"

#, c-format
msgid ""
"IT SEEMS AS IF THIS THEME REPOSITORY IS CORRUPT, WHICH COULD HAVE BEEN "
"CAUSED BY AN INTERRUPTION OF A PREVIOUS DOWNLOAD OR UPDATE, FOR EXAMPLE IF "
"THE ES-DE PROCESS WAS KILLED. A FRESH DOWNLOAD IS REQUIRED AND THE OLD THEME "
"DIRECTORY \"%s\" WILL BE RENAMED TO \"%s_CORRUPT_DISABLED\""
msgstr ""
"ČINI SE KAO DA JE OVAJ REPOZITORIJ TEMA OŠTEĆEN, ŠTO JE MOGLO BITI "
"UZROKOVANO PREKIDANOM PRETHODNOG PREUZIMANJA ILI AŽURIRANJA, NA PRIMJER AKO "
"JE ES-DE PROCES ZAUSTAVLJEN. POTREBNO JE NOVO PREUZIMANJE I STARI DIREKTORIJ "
"TEME \"%s\" BIT ĆE PREIMENOVAN U \"%s_CORRUPT_DISABLED\""

#, c-format
msgid ""
"IT SEEMS AS IF THIS IS A SHALLOW REPOSITORY WHICH MEANS THAT IT HAS BEEN "
"DOWNLOADED USING SOME OTHER TOOL THAN THIS THEME DOWNLOADER. A FRESH "
"DOWNLOAD IS REQUIRED AND THE OLD THEME DIRECTORY \"%s\" WILL BE RENAMED TO "
"\"%s_DISABLED\""
msgstr ""
"ČINI SE KAO DA JE OVO PLITKO REPOZITORIJ ŠTO ZNAČI DA JE PREUZETO POMOĆU "
"NEKOG DRUGOG ALATA, A NE OVOG PROGRAMA ZA PREUZIMANJE TEMA. POTREBNO JE "
"SVJEŽE PREUZIMANJE, A STARI DIREKTORIJ TEME \"%s\" BIT ĆE PREIMENOVAN U "
"\"%s_DISABLED\""

#, c-format
msgid ""
"IT SEEMS AS IF THIS IS A DIVERGED REPOSITORY WHICH USUALLY MEANS THERE IS AN "
"UPSTREAM MERGE CONFLICT THAT NEEDS TO BE RESOLVED BY THE THEME DEVELOPER. A "
"FRESH DOWNLOAD IS REQUIRED AND THE OLD THEME DIRECTORY \"%s\" WILL BE "
"RENAMED TO \"%s_DIVERGED_DISABLED\""
msgstr ""
"OVO IZGLEDA KAO DIVERGIRANI REPOZITORIJ ŠTO OBIČNO ZNAČI DA POSTOJI SUKOB "
"PRI SPAJANJU UZVODNOG PROGRAMA KOJI RAZVOJ TEME TREBA RIJEŠITI. POTREBNO JE "
"NOVO PREUZIMANJE, A STARI DIREKTORIJ TEME \"%s\" BIT ĆE PREIMENOVAN U "
"\"%s_DIVERGED_DISABLED\""

#, c-format
msgid ""
"THE LOCALLY CLONED REPOSITORY CONTAINS THE WRONG URL WHICH NORMALLY MEANS "
"THE THEME HAS BEEN MOVED TO A NEW GIT SITE. A FRESH DOWNLOAD IS REQUIRED AND "
"THE OLD THEME DIRECTORY \"%s\" WILL BE RENAMED TO \"%s_WRONG_URL_DISABLED\""
msgstr ""
"LOKALNO KLONIRANI REPOZITORIJ SADRŽI POGREŠAN URL ŠTO NORMALNO ZNAČI DA JE "
"TEMA PREMJEŠTENA NA NOVU GIT STRANICU. POTREBNO JE SVJEŽE PREUZIMANJE I "
"STARI DIREKTOR TEME \"%s\" BIT ĆE PREIMENOVAN U \"%s_WRONG_URL_DISABLED\""

